00:01:00.370 --> 00:01:03.750
He was Director of the
Center for Applied Economics

00:01:03.750 --> 00:01:06.180
at the Lagos Business School.

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:09.370
He has served in senior
positions in government

00:01:09.370 --> 00:01:12.420
as an advisor to the
president of Nigeria,

00:01:12.420 --> 00:01:15.530
the private sector
