00:43:37.400 --> 00:43:38.840
grew up on "Patito's Gang."

00:43:38.840 --> 00:43:40.330
I feel good about that.

00:43:40.330 --> 00:43:43.900
It was just about creating
a marketplace of ideas.

00:43:43.900 --> 00:43:49.210
Unless a nation can get good
quality conversation going,

00:43:49.210 --> 00:43:52.290
