00:44:06.060 --> 00:44:07.636
When I produced--
when we started,

00:44:07.636 --> 00:44:10.770
I wanted for it to be the
best possible quality.

00:44:10.770 --> 00:44:16.420
In fact, the first director was
American who lived in Nigeria.

00:44:16.420 --> 00:44:18.504
And we had, in the
then director general,

00:44:18.504 --> 00:44:19.920
or immediate past
director general

00:44:19.920 --> 00:44:23.360
of NTA engineer
[INAUDIBLE] man who

00:44:23.360 --> 00:44:26.450
told me, after the first two
episodes, and said to me,

00:44:26.450 --> 00:44:28.410
