00:48:58.630 --> 00:48:59.870
travelling a different track.

00:49:07.710 --> 00:49:11.080
PAT UTOMI: Now about the guy who
has all his money in dollars.

00:49:11.080 --> 00:49:13.580
First of all, there are so
many foolish people in Nigeria,

00:49:13.580 --> 00:49:16.988
because I consider
